OL,3,CSenior police officer sacked for
OL,4,Cpunching two women
OL,6,FA senior police officer with a
OL,7,Fdistinguished career tackling violence
OL,8,Fagainst women has been sacked for
OL,9,Fassaulting two women while off duty.
OL,11,FThe incident took place while
OL,12,FInspector Tola Munro was serving as a
OL,13,Fneighbourhood officer in south Bristol
OL,14,Fin May 2023.
OL,16,FDue to the serious nature of the
OL,17,Fallegations, Avon and Somerset Police
OL,18,Freferred themselves to the Independent
OL,19,FOffice for Police Conduct.
