OL,3,CSenior police officer sacked for
OL,4,Cpunching two women
OL,6,FA panel, chaired by a Legally
OL,7,FQualified Chair who is independent of
OL,8,Fpolicing, ruled that Inspector Tola
OL,9,FMunro's actions amounted to gross
OL,10,Fmisconduct.
OL,12,FAs well as being dismissed without
OL,13,Fnotice, he will also be added to the
OL,14,Fbarred list to prevent him from
OL,15,Fserving as a police officer again.
OL,17,FThe panel ruled that Inspector Munro
OL,18,Fhad breached two standards of
OL,19,Fprofessional behaviour, in relation to
OL,20,Fdiscreditable conduct, as well as
OL,21,Fauthority, respect and courtesy.
