OL,3,CSenior police officer sacked for
OL,4,Cpunching two women
OL,6,FHe was suspended while the criminal
OL,7,Fand misconduct investigations were
OL,8,Fcarried out. Munro denies the
OL,9,Fallegations and says he was acting in
OL,10,Fself defence.
OL,12,FGwent Police carried out a criminal
OL,13,Finvestigation into the incident,
OL,14,Fculminating in the case being referred
OL,15,Fto the Crown Prosecution Service,
OL,16,Fwhich deemed there was insufficient
OL,17,Fevidence for there to be a realistic
OL,18,Fprospect of a successful prosecution.
