OL,3,CSenior police officer sacked for
OL,4,Cpunching two women
OL,6,F"Ultimately, there is no place in
OL,7,Fpolicing for an officer who is found
OL,8,Fto have assaulted any member of the
OL,9,Fpublic.
OL,11,F"Whether on or off-duty, officers and
OL,12,Fstaff must adhere to the standards
OL,13,Fexpected of anyone serving in policing
OL,14,Fand Inspector Munro failed to do this.
OL,16,F"As an organisation we have carried
OL,17,Fout a huge amount of work in recent
OL,18,Fyears around the topic of violence
OL,19,Fagainst women and girls.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
