OL,4,Cpunching two women
OL,6,F"Inspector Munro's actions have
OL,7,Fundermined those efforts and will
OL,8,Flikely damage public confidence in
OL,9,Fpolicing.
OL,11,F"We hope the public can see from the
OL,12,Factions we have taken that these
OL,13,Fallegations have been taken seriously
OL,14,Ffrom the moment we learned of them.
OL,16,F"The public's trust in policing is
OL,17,Fdependent on rooting out any officer,
OL,18,Fno matter their rank or experience,
OL,19,Fwho should not be serving the public.
